Hi <%= @user.first_name %>,

Welcome to Freedom Podcasting — your show is ready to launch.

Here are three things to do first:

1. CREATE YOUR PODCAST
   Add your show title, artwork, and description so your feed is ready to
   submit to Apple Podcasts and Spotify.

2. PUBLISH YOUR FIRST EPISODE
   Upload your audio file, write your show notes, and hit Publish. Your
   RSS feed updates automatically.

3. SUBMIT TO THE DIRECTORIES
   Copy your RSS feed URL from the podcast settings page and submit it to
   Apple Podcasts, Spotify, and any other directories you want.

